`googlesearch` - library
`search` - function in the `googlesearch` library
`stop` - parameter of the `search` function
source.name: googlesearchLibrary
source.text: The <<<googlesearch>>> library has function called <<<search>>> that takes a user <<<query>>> and runs a Google search. It also has a parameter called <<<stop>>> that can limit the number of top search results to fetch.
